.TH "CITADEL" "1" "Jun 2026" "AceTeam" "Citadel CLI Manual"

.SH NAME
citadel-nodes - List all compute nodes in your AceTeam fabric


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcitadel nodes [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Connects to the Nexus control plane and retrieves a list of all
registered compute nodes, showing their status, IP address, and last-seen time.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for nodes

.PP
\fB--json\fP[=false]
	Output in JSON format


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB--no-color\fP[=false]
	Disable colorized output


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBcitadel(1)\fP
